cs.MA, cs.GT, cs.LG, cs.NE, cs.SY

This paper deals with the optimization of traffic networks with mixed vehicle autonomy, which involves game theory, optimization, and control systems. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.MA (Multiagent Systems). The paper also discusses pricing mechanisms, which falls under the category of mechanism design and game theory, making cs.GT (Game Theory) another likely category. The paper also involves optimization of social delay, which falls under the category of optimization, making cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) likely categories. Finally, the paper also involves control systems, making cs.SY (Systems and Control) a possible category.
